<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
    <title>Cocktail Gallery</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    
    <link href="dist/css/gallery.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "gallery"%>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,900" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0" />
</head>
<style>

</style>


<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-item">
            <a href="../index.html" style="font-family:'Romantic Beach', Cursive; font-size: 23px; font-weight: 300;">
                CockTailor</a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-right">
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="makeyourown.html">칵테일 만들기</a></div>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="recommendation.html">칵테일 추천</a></div>
            <div class="nav-item"><a href="gallery.html">칵테일 갤러리</a></div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="gallery" class="light-bg">
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <h2>칵테일 갤러리</h2>
                        <p>여러분이 만든 칵테일을 살펴보세요</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                     
            <div id="gallery-content">
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag("blue.png") %>
                        <img src="images/blue.png" class="img-responsive" />
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">나만의 칵테일 블루</p>
                            <p class="description">맛있는 칵테일이래요 -by HS</p>


                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag("purple.png") %>
                        
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">블랙인가 퍼플인가</p>
                            <p class="description">시크한 퍼플칵테일도 필요하죠 -by SJ</p>

                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag('images-2.jpeg') %>
                        
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">레드자몽 위스키 한잔</p>
                            <p class="description">최애 레드에 자몽에 알코올까지 -by MC</p>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag('images.jpeg') %>
                        
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">키위를 기억해</p>
                            <p class="description">새콤달콤 -by HJ</p>

                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag('images-4.jpeg') %>
                        <img src="images/images-4.jpeg" class="img-responsive" />
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">아이셔</p>
                            <p class="description">먹지 마세요, 피부에 양보하세요</p>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag('images-3.jpeg') %>
                        
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">바다맛, 맛있기만 한걸</p>
                            <p class="description">세상에 하나뿐인 칵테일</p>

                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag("barbackground.jpg") %>
                        <img src="images/barbackground.jpg" alt="img02" class="img-responsive" />
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">나만의 칵테일 블루</p>
                            <p class="description">맛있는 칵테일이래요 -by HS</p>

                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag("cocktails.jpg") %>
                        <img src="images/cocktails.jpeg" alt="img02" class="img-responsive" />
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">시크블랙 칵테일인가</p>
                            <p class="description">시크한 블랙칵테일도 필요하죠 -by SJ</p>


                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>

                <div class="gallery-item">
                    <figure class="fig">
                        <%= image_tag("cocktails.jpeg") %>
                        
                        <figcaption>
                            <p class="figure-title">블랙</p>
                            <p class="description">시크한 블랙칵테일도 필요하죠 -by SJ</p>

                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        </div>
    </section>


</body>

</html>